{"tid":1242191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實廢老/外媒覺得送中條例同撤回無分別先係好事","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T04:25:14.000Z","uid":168703,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c17154e36b20bc7d0b330eeb4a3e6f2608607ee7","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"睇到其他post話外媒報導以為等同撤回，一班中立同廢老又話而家都停咗啦仲搞乜鬼，<br />\n講真佢地咁樣以為先係好事，<br />\n因為如果真係有日佢想重推，勇武派就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出師有命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家集中目標救學生先，一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815329bf4633e22407f454aabeccd4765547dc23","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e7be099f2957711581d31879fa2953eb508aa20","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7866e37adc1c1e1f29c7cc6844679c26bac3c37","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b298447cd153abf93c647c2d6717edfbccd7a620","tid":1242191,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於 追究黑警濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先講建議：<br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fd4fdb942ed348f73b0e2ab87a42ba35cf1e58","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"到時外媒同中立人士就會知呢個政府反口覆舌，連警狗都唔會支持佢地"},{"pid":"70c32642e35972aa4926b4b0f8add4ab39aaa02f","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0349af1a0e8f834685b4fc312b615f8375995ed","tid":1242191,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"我都覺，無謂浪費時間力量同佢玩語言偽術"},{"pid":"a1898f1fa94aa9b566444a20e60ec83084d389b7","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b1fa98f83ad2178881c5d3c077ed8277b8045de","tid":1242191,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57c6e346f3db595e